Summary: This is the 3rd strange sphere "dot" I have in my pictures. Notice the cloud formation like an eye.
divs: Sighting DetailsI love the weather but this is the 3rd strange sphere or 'dot' I've captured in my picture. Also I notice an 'eye' cloud formation in two photos with this latest one has the eye and the sphere together! I have repasted the other two so that all 3 pictures are viewable together although they were taken on 3 different ocasions and all this year. If anyone has seen similar please share thanks, mufon!
